<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=6503&amp;p=28362#p28362"><![CDATA[
Use the &quot;Tree item spacing&quot; setting in the Navigation Pane tab.<br />Keep in mind that in Windows 10 the spacing setting is multiplied by 3. So -1 means &quot;reduce by 3 pixels&quot;.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2">Ivo</a> — Sun Aug 07, 2016 7:43 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
